Open the Time & Motion Tracker file.

Go to the summary section (cells E7 to E11).

Fill all mandatory details in E7â€“E11.

Do not leave any summary cell blank.

Go to the task entry area (rows 19 to 50).

Enter the Broad Step for the task.

Enter the Step Name for the task.

Broad Step and Step Name are mandatory.

Select the row where you want to start the task.

Click the Start button.

Start Time will be captured automatically.

The running row will turn green.

Only one task can run at a time.

You cannot start a new task until the running task is ended.

If you need a break, click the Pause button.

The task will be paused.

The row color will change to yellow.

You cannot pause the same task multiple times.

Click the Resume button to continue the task.

The task will resume from the paused time.

The row color will turn green again.

Click the End button after task completion.

End Time and total duration will be calculated automatically.

To delete tasks, select one or multiple Step Names.

Click Clear Line to remove all related data.

After completing all tasks, click the Archive button.

Choose the folder and save the file.

All data will be cleared automatically for next use.
